reviews.text: Nice song mall with a variety of understated and slightly alternative brands. The central area is often used for events (celebrity signing sessions, promotion activities, etc) on weekends which adds flavour to the visit. Most shops and restaurants here won't break the bank either but do expect a crowd!
I always pay a visit to this place because of Marks & Spencer.  Most shops in this mall sell apparel items and accessories.  There are restaurants on some floors and a playplace for kids.
fun mall near Victoria park with coffe place,movies and restaurants etc

Heaps of shops, but the fail mark for me is that the elevator from the ground floor up to the first floor to access the regular elevator for the rest of the centre shuts at 8pm. I'm quite disappointed that I could not properly wheel my elderly father properly here. To close the elevator at 8pm rather than closing time of the centre is disgraceful.
Excellent, has a cinema, a Marks and Spencers and a Genki sushi, what more do I need?

reviews.text: Nice song mall with a variety of understated and slightly alternative brands. The central area is often used for events (celebrity signing sessions, promotion activities, etc) on weekends which adds flavour to the visit. Most shops and restaurants here won't break the bank either but do expect a crowd!

我對皇室堡商場評分極高！
首先因爲皇室堡交通方便，好近港鐵站👍
而皇室堡內既商店都唔算高消費，價錢適中，商場內店舖種類亦都好多樣化～吃飲玩樂應有盡有！
我覺得這個商場十分適合一家大細去逛逛！因為裡面有「美國冒險樂園」和「玩具反斗城」還有另外幾間兒童玩具店，所以我覺得十分適合家庭樂～
除此之外，皇室堡經常有舉辦唔同活動展覽等，多數都是跟一些卡通合作，記得曾經有鬆弛熊，櫻桃小丸子，正能量企鵝等等既商場佈置，有時還會有期間限定店！絕對不可以錯過！
另外皇室堡平時的佈置都有一些很可愛的牆紙，十分適合小朋友！
推薦有小孩的家庭去～
銅鑼灣區的皇室堡，我很久已沒有行了，近期已改變很多，很多適合年青人的商店及名店，中間亦可作小型活動及表演，帶動不少青春氣息。
多左不同元素，但樓底偏矮有點焗促感。

result.name: Watami Japanese Casual Restaurant

reviews.text: Don’t miss their delicious Okonomiyaki and other delicious japanese cuisines 🥰

Service really bizarre here..

First time we came, the waiter seated us at some weirdly elevated "high chairs" and "high table". When we wanted to take the normal ones instead, the waiter just sent us out and asked us to queue again. But the restaurant was only half full! And so we left.

Second time we came, the waitress seated us at the sofa bench. The whole bench had back panel except the one at the side and we were seated there... and the place was even less than half full this time.

Been to so many different Watamis in HK and this is the only one that had us dumbfounded.
Small is size and overall it’s too salty. It’s overrated.

Next to the Grand Windsor cinerma.
Spacious shop, food quality ok but not high standard.
Set lunch ranges fm $5x

This Japanese Restaurant is located at the 4th Floor of Windsor. 

There are choices of Japanese Foods. From Chicken, Pork, Beef to Seafood and sushi. Not much sashimi choices.  

They offers Hot Pot. The seafood with Hiroshima Oysters Hot Pot is very good. 

They also offers rice in stone pot. 

Place is nicely design. 

I always include in my review service staff. A restaurant needs good food and good service. The restaurant staff is not attentive enough for customer needs.

reviews.text: 食物不錯，三四人談天說地可以到來三四五個鐘，ㄧ個很好的地方吧

貴 食物普通 無coupon唔會幫襯
無乜客所以不用等位
常光顧，只是服務水準仍有待改善
星期六下午叫咗個三種壽司盛，同埋豚骨醬油拉麵，牛油果蝦沙律，個人覺得麻麻，啲面好鹹得一塊塊豬，啲壽司上邊果塊魚生又薄又唔新鮮，沙律就ok
Don’t miss their delicious Okonomiyaki and other delicious japanese cuisines 🥰
